desc_long							评测						“A super comic-style adventure for the whole family with many funny details and allusions”78/100 – Adventure-Archiv“Think interactive cartoons with clever, sometimes downright hard, puzzles set a friendly, postmodern, fart-joke environment, and you have Fatman.”Tap-Repeatedly (Four Fat Chicks)“It's a fun romp that doesn't take itself seriously despite the critical problems you must solve.”B+ – GameBoomers												关于这款游戏							To the Fat Mobile, let's go !! You are the crime fighter for the city of Shadowlawn. Just when you're complaining about how dull things have been, a supervillain named Toxicman is created from a botched act of corporate sabotage. It is up to you, then, to tear yourself away from food long enough to save the city from certain destruction...There is fun, laughs and even some heroic moments to be had in The Adventures of Fatman: Toxic Revenge! Now available at budget price for Steam collectors, the first commercial AGS game returns to your screens. This special edition includes extra easter eggs & an improved ending. Additional special features, trading cards & soundtrack are also included!Yesterday's technology, today !! + Comedy adventure game suitable for all (some mild comic violence)+ Parody point & click with a retro kick+ Full English voice acting + Interesting locations to visit & fun characters to meet+ Hand-drawn art & animations, original soundtrack+ Designer commentary in-game+ Easy mode (normal, hints & retries) or hard mode (no saves, no hints + sudden death)						
